net.sf.mmm.search.base.config

Class AbstractSearchConfigurationBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mmm.search.base.config.AbstractSearchConfigurationBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SearchConfiguration
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SearchConfigurationBean, SearchIndexerConfigurationBean

    public abstract class AbstractSearchConfigurationBean
extends Object
implements SearchConfiguration
    This is the abstract base-implementation of SearchConfiguration as JAXB-ready Java-Bean.
    Unfortunately JAXB does not properly support generics so we cannot use a generic for polymorphism of SearchSourceBean.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
